The paper proposes a novel approach for generating satisfying assignments and counting the total number of satisfying assignments for Boolean satisfiability problems. This falls under the category of algorithms and complexity (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), and machine learning (cs.LG).
